OL,3,CTehran in 'weak position', says White
OL,4,CHouse as Iran tightens grip on strait
OL,6,FDonald Trump is holding the cards, the
OL,7,FWhite House has insisted as Iran
OL,8,Ftightened its hold on the strategic
OL,9,FStrait of Hormuz by seizing two ships.
OL,11,FWhile the US president extended the
OL,12,Ffragile truce to enable Tehran to come
OL,13,Fup with a "unified" proposal, he has
OL,14,Fmaintained the naval blockade of the
OL,15,Fcountry's ports.
OL,17,FThis has led Iran to accuse the White
OL,18,FHouse of a "flagrant breach of the
OL,19,Fceasefire".
OL,26,@uD@KOUuD@SO]zD@LOU{D@JO]
