OL,3,CTehran in 'weak position', says White
OL,4,CHouse as Iran tightens grip on strait
OL,6,FThe stand-off means the strait ` a
OL,7,Fmaritime pinchpoint ` is still
OL,8,Feffectively closed meaning ongoing
OL,9,Fpain to the global economy.
OL,11,FThe conflict, triggered by joint US-
OL,12,FIsraeli strikes at the end of
OL,13,FFebruary, had already sent energy
OL,14,Fprices soaring and hiked the cost of
OL,15,Fother goods.
OL,17,FThe impasse has cast further doubt on
OL,18,Fthe prospect of talks aimed at
OL,19,Fsecuring a lasting end to hostilities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
