OL,3,CTehran in 'weak position', says White
OL,4,CHouse as Iran tightens grip on strait
OL,6,FMeanwhile, military planners from a
OL,7,Fcoalition of countries were due to
OL,8,Fcontinue meeting in London on Thursday
OL,9,Fas part of plans for a UK and France-
OL,10,Fled defensive mission to keep the
OL,11,Fcritical waterway open once the Iran
OL,12,Fwar is over.
OL,14,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper has
OL,15,Fsaid Britain wanted to see a
OL,16,F"comprehensive settlement" and a "full
OL,17,Freopening" of the key shipping route
OL,18,Fwithout restrictions or tolls.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@ZO]xD@bOUyD@JO]
