OL,3,CTehran in 'weak position', says White
OL,4,CHouse as Iran tightens grip on strait
OL,6,FIn a separate development, it was also
OL,7,Freported a top envoy to the US
OL,8,Fpresident has asked Fifa to replace
OL,9,FIran with Italy in the upcoming World
OL,10,FCup.
OL,12,FThe Financial Times said the move was
OL,13,Faimed at repairing relations between
OL,14,FMr Trump and the Italian prime
OL,15,Fminister Giorgia Meloni after his
OL,16,Fattacks on the Pope over the war.
