OL,3,CTehran in 'weak position', says White
OL,4,CHouse as Iran tightens grip on strait
OL,6,FIn a late social media post on
OL,7,FTuesday, Mr Trump said the Tehran
OL,8,Fregime was "seriously fractured" and
OL,9,Fhad agreed to a request by Pakistani
OL,10,Fmediators "to hold our Attack on the
OL,11,FCountry of Iran until such time as
OL,12,Ftheir leaders and representatives can
OL,13,Fcome up with a unified proposal".
OL,15,FWhite House press secretary Karoline
OL,16,FLeavitt said: "There's obviously a lot
OL,17,Fof internal division. This is a battle
OL,18,Fbetween the pragmatists and the
OL,19,Fhardliners in Iran right now and the
OL,20,Fpresident wants a unified response."
OL,26,@pD@LOUpD@`O]rD@KOUuD@`O]xD@OOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
