OL,3,CTehran in 'weak position', says White
OL,4,CHouse as Iran tightens grip on strait
OL,6,FHailing the success of the US
OL,7,Fblockade, she said: "We are completely
OL,8,Fstrangling their economy through this
OL,9,Fblockade. They're losing 500 million
OL,10,Fdollars a day."
OL,12,FShe said the country's main oil export
OL,13,Fterminal was "completely full", as a
OL,14,Fresult of the bar on shipping.
OL,16,FWith no new end date set for the
OL,17,Fextended ceasefire, Ms Leavitt added:
OL,18,F"The United States maintains control
OL,19,Fover this situation, leverage over the
OL,20,FIranian regime.
OL,26,@oD@UOUrD@OO]uD@NOUuD@^O]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
