OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776906184
OL,3,CTehran in 'weak position', says White
OL,4,CHouse as Iran tightens grip on strait
OL,6,F"Not only have they been significantly
OL,7,Fweakened and obliterated militarily,
OL,8,Fbut they are losing economically and
OL,9,Ffinancially every single moment that
OL,10,Fpasses with this blockade."
OL,12,FShe went on: "Ultimately, he (Mr
OL,13,FTrump) will dictate the timetable. He
OL,14,Fis satisfied with the naval blockade,
OL,15,Fand he understands that Iran is in a
OL,16,Fvery weak position and the cards are
OL,17,Fin President Trump's hands right now
OL,18,Fon.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@[O]tD@NOU
