OL,3,CTehran in 'weak position', says White
OL,4,CHouse as Iran tightens grip on strait
OL,6,F"The president chose to extend the
OL,7,Fceasefire because it's Iran who need
OL,8,Fto get their act together."
OL,10,FBut Tehran has insisted the blockade
OL,11,Fmust be lifted.
OL,13,FThe speaker of Iran's parliament and
OL,14,Fthe country's chief negotiator
OL,15,FMohammad Baqer Qalibaf said: "You did
OL,16,Fnot achieve your goals through
OL,17,Fmilitary aggression and you will not
OL,18,Fachieve them by bullying either. The
OL,19,Fonly way is recognising the Iranian
OL,20,Fpeople's rights."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@[O]wD@^OU|D@QO]
