OL,3,CTehran in 'weak position', says White
OL,4,CHouse as Iran tightens grip on strait
OL,6,FIn a further show of defiance, large
OL,7,Fcrowds turned out for a parade in
OL,8,FTehran, where the regime put on show
OL,9,Fsome of its ballistic missiles, while
OL,10,Fbanners proclaimed the strait was
OL,11,F"Indefinitely under Iran's Control"
OL,12,Fand "Trump could not do a damn thing".
